** IMPORTANT ***

  This distribution *MUST* be installed under the /home/mordor 
directory in order to run.  If you want to change this you will have 
to alter mordor.cf to accomodate the new paths.
  If you are running this under Win95/NT you *MUST* install it under the 
/home/mordor directory.

 --------------- ------ -----
  Binaries are provided for Linux ELF (2.0.29) and Win32 (95 & NT).

  This distribution can be compiled under Win95/NT, Linux, FreeBSD,
SunOS, NeXT, IRIX, ULTRIX, HPUX, SCO, and requires that you have at least 
3M+ RAM (8M+ recommended), and around 10-15M of HD space. 
